9, 501.4, 458.3, 524.5]}, {"text": "6,432,881", "bbox": [490.9, 501.4, 574.3, 524.5]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [595.8, 501.4, 606.2, 524.5]}, {"text": "5,999,563", "bbox": [636.8, 501.4, 720.1, 524.5]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [741.7, 501.4, 752.1, 524.5]}, {"text": "5,781,852", "bbox": [784.7, 501.4, 868.0, 524.5]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [889.6, 501.4, 900.0, 524.5]}, {"text": "5,786,681", "bbox": [932.6, 501.4, 1015.9, 524.5]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [1037.5, 501.4, 1047.9, 524.5]}, {"text": "6,017,569", "bbox": [1080.5, 501.4, 1163.9, 524.5]}, {"text": "HDFS offers wholesale financing to the Company’s independent dealers. Wholesale loans to dealers are generally", "bbox": [151.0, 553.8, 1109.6, 576.9]}, {"text": "secured by financed inventory or property and are originated in the U.S. and Canada.", "bbox": [104.2, 578.8, 817.5, 601.9]}, {"text": "HDFS provides retail financial services to customers of the Company’s independent dealers in the U.S. and Canada. The", "bbox": [154.2, 622.6, 1163.4, 645.6]}, {"text": "origination of retail loans is a separate and distinct transaction between HDFS and the retail customer, unrelated to the", "bbox": [104.2, 647.6, 1093.8, 670.6]}, {"text": "Company’s sale of product to its dealers. Retail finance receivables consist of secured promissory notes and installment loans.", "bbox": [104.2, 672.6, 1159.6, 695.6]}, {"text": "HDFS holds either titles or liens on titles to vehicles financed by promissory notes and installment loans. As of December 31,", "bbox": [104.2, 697.6, 1155.5, 720.6]}, {"text": "2014 and 2013, approximately 12% of gross outstanding finance receivables were originated in Texas; there were no other state", "bbox": [104.2, 722.6, 1172.6, 745.6]}, {"text": "that accounted for more than 10%.", "bbox": [104.2, 747.6, 392.3, 770.6]}, {"text": "Unused lines of credit extended to the Company's wholesale finance customers totaled $1.01 billion at both", "bbox": [154.2, 791.3, 1054.1, 814.4]}, {"text": "December 31, 2014 and 2013. Approved but unfunded retail finance loans totaled $168.7 million and $149.8 million at", "bbox": [104.2, 816.3, 1100.5, 839.4]}, {"text": "December 31, 2014 and 2013, respectively.", "bbox": [104.2, 841.3, 465.0, 864.4]}, {"text": "Wholesale finance receivables are related primarily to motorcycles and related parts and accessories sales to independent", "bbox": [154.2, 885.1, 1167.8, 908.1]}, {"text": "Harley-Davidson dealers and are generally contractually due within one year. Retail finance receivables are primarily related to", "bbox": [104.2, 910.1, 1170.9, 933.1]}, {"text": "sales of motorcycles to the dealers’ customers. On December 31, 2014, contractual maturities of finance receivables were as", "bbox": [104.2, 935.1, 1143.4, 958.1]}, {"text": "follows (in thousands):", "bbox": [104.2, 960.1, 301.0, 983.1]}, {"text": "United States", "bbox": [707.7, 1002.2, 802.6, 1020.6]}, {"text": "Canada", "bbox": [895.1, 1002.2, 950.7, 1020.6]}, {"text": "Total", "bbox": [1072.4, 1002.2, 1110.4, 1020.6]}, {"text": "2015", "bbox": [110.4, 1026.6, 152.1, 1049.7]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [681.2, 1026.6, 691.7, 1049.7]}, {"text": "1,856,097", "bbox": [745.1, 1026.6, 828.4, 1049.7]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [850.0, 1026.6, 860.4, 1049.7]}, {"text": "86,518", "bbox": [937.8, 1026.6, 995.1, 1049.7]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [1016.7, 1026.6, 1027.1, 1049.7]}, {"text": "1,942,615", "bbox": [1080.5, 1026.6, 1163.9, 1049.7]}, {"text": "2016", "bbox": [110.4, 1055.8, 152.1, 1078.8]}, {"text": "1,029,075", "bbox": [745.1, 1055.8, 828.4, 1078.8]}, {"text": "40,378", "bbox": [937.8, 1055.8, 995.1, 1078.8]}, {"text": "1,069,453", "bbox": [1080.5, 1055.8, 1163.9, 1078.8]}, {"text": "2017", "bbox": [110.4, 1084.9, 152.1, 1108.0]}, {"text": "1,155,891", "bbox": [745.1, 1084.9, 828.4, 1108.0]}, {"text": "45,041", "bbox": [937.8, 1084.9, 995.1, 1108.0]}, {"text": "1,200,932", "bbox": [1080.5, 1084.9, 1163.9, 1108.0]}, {"text": "2018", "bbox": [110.4, 1114.1, 152.1, 1137.2]}, {"text": "